{"about_the_game":"Galaia is a small Action-Adventure Roguelite made with love for both roguelite fans and newcomers to the genre!<br><br>Centuries have passed since The Flood destroyed the mighty kingdom of Galaia. Atop of the wreckage, only the Last Ruins remain, and among them the answers to what happened.<br><br>Venture time and time again into the ever-changing ruins of Galaia defeating enemies, exploring enigmatic locations, and uncovering secrets until you collect all the powerful Relics hidden inside!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A COZY ROGUELITE</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/chest.gif?t=1721318430\" /><br>Galaia is very <strong>welcoming to newcomers</strong> to the genre while still offering <strong>challenges to the most veteran roguelike players</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FAST AND FUN COMBAT</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/combat.gif?t=1721318430\" /><br>Galaia's combat is straight up shooter fun, very focused on <strong>mobility and synergies</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MORE THAN MEETS THE EYE</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/skull.gif?t=1721318430\" /><br>Not everything is combat! The mysterious ruins hide many <strong>secrets and collectibles</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>COME AND JOIN THE ADVENTURE!</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/flood.gif?t=1721318430\" /><br>What are you waiting for? Galaia awaits!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Developer's Note</h2><i>Galaia has been developed by <strong>just one person</strong> over 4 years! As such, it has been impossible for me to add as many content to the game as the other amazing big roguelike titles. However <strong>lots of love</strong> and care have been put in this game, so others can experience the game that I always wanted to make and play.<br><br>I'm very conscious of player's time and money, so I tried to price the game fairly for what it has to offer. Expect around a short fun game with a very replayable structure. </i><br><br>I sincerely hope you enjoy the game as much as I enjoyed making it!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"An Ancient Treasure","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/6a50c2836f9be065221be415293fd27d472aa5d6.jpg"},{"name":"A Powerful Item","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/7d870c54167784762abd1673baaedf282b67b12f.jpg"},{"name":"Secrets Revealed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/1988603902c4d8b4a50261d2dd7cb8231c092842.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/62009b46202df3674a1c99ea89ad58f79b70a0e3.jpg"},{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/4e2e74ff4e88fb9dfc329d1e8e0064252853a26f.jpg"},{"name":"Legend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/ae0fe911ff79153612a8156ea69082d146075fc5.jpg"},{"name":"Pure Greed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/b8a736383d9f70d805d5582ccbc08b7f364b4bc2.jpg"},{"name":"Memento of the Princess","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/eae970a3eae1a3286bbba2aa2b1095c31b1f243b.jpg"},{"name":"Clumsy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/e2e1bb02c4d3a475367f54af432a5d3001401713.jpg"},{"name":"Touched by the Sun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1625930/443fb040d5e539b671c41d32057989f268a0f080.jpg"}],"total":21},"background":"htt